         <p>In some cases the weather sensors listed above have been linked
           to data loggers where, in most instances, comparable data may
           be obtained (see <a href=\"#placeholder\">Appendix E<\/a>). However, a broken wire or power
           outage may render automated data useless, so manual observations
           are still preferred as a baseline.<\/p>
